      "content": "yeah exactly. it's like the more i try to be okay, the more i realize there's nothing to actually be okay for. like, what's the point of even trying to fix things when the whole world just seems set on making me feel small? sometimes i just think about how much easier it would be if i could just... stop. if i could just exit this whole thing so i wouldn't have to deal with the noise anymore. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace.",
